{"tid":1697360,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"各大學校長的春袋就係捐款人","createTime":"2019-11-06T21:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T16:30:15.000Z","uid":263648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c5c79faf98bafa0be22b01b27009c3c74959eae3","tid":1697360,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T21:10:30.000Z","msg":"大學校長每年都想R盡 FUNDINGS<br />\n要去聽中聯辦講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔聽話，班親土共背景的捐款人就唔肯再捐款<br />\n佢地驚既係，呢間大學無FUNDING，會益咗其他大學<br />\n其實可以一招合縱連橫，迫佢地對抗秦暴政<br />\n就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>將大學紅色捐款人挖出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最理想係針對同時捐幾間U的捐款人，放大佢地曾經奶共黑歷史，最好係過去五個月曾發生，連結返個運動</strong></span></span><br />\n好似美心、福建360咁，擺佢地上枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾間U學生會一齊<br />\n高調放大呢班紅色/親土共捐款人的惡行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">趕走大學校長(而家中大校長已經CONNECT咗)的後台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令佢地齊齊無咗紅色捐款人</span></span></strong><br />\n到時撐唔撐學生唔會有分別<br />\nd校長就會撐落去<br />\n攞返個道德高地做尾彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當三、四個校長都係咁，就可以重整返大學個場<br />\n穩住後方支援，長期玩落去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，驅逐共黨</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4de477bc89f456944b71831fede7a04b161f51","tid":1697360,"uid":131326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T22:00:33.000Z","msg":"黑警毅進狗，全家不得好死落地獄返大灣"},{"pid":"39444480ed4607529d8dadc076adc3deb57e8145","tid":1697360,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a4de477bc89f456944b71831fede7a04b161f51","tid":1697360,"uid":131326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-1